</span> 標題：麻、亞麻、細麻布（linen）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֵטוּן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’etun)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:16\">PRO 7:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bad)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:42\">EXO 28:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:28\">EXO 39:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:3\">LEV 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:3\">LEV 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:23\">LEV 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:32\">LEV 16:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1SA 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:18\">1SA 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14\">2SA 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:27\">1CH 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:11\">EZK 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:2\">EZK 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:6\">EZK 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:7\">EZK 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:5\">DAN 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:6\">DAN 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:7\">DAN 12:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בּוּץ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： buts)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:21\">1CH 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:27\">1CH 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13\">2CH 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:14\">2CH 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:12\">2CH 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:15\">EST 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">סָדִין</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：sadin（參)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:12\">JDG 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:13\">JDG 14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:24\">PRO 31:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:23\">ISA 3:23</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： פֵּשֶׁת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pishteh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:48\">LEV 13:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:52\">LEV 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:59\">LEV 13:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:11\">DEU 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:1\">JER 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:17\">EZK 44:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:18\">EZK 44:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:18\">EZK 44:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שֵׁשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:42\">GEN 41:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:4\">EXO 25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31\">EXO 26:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:36\">EXO 26:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:9\">EXO 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:16\">EXO 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:18\">EXO 27:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:6\">EXO 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:8\">EXO 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:6\">EXO 35:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:23\">EXO 35:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:35\">EXO 35:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8\">EXO 36:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:35\">EXO 36:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:37\">EXO 36:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:9\">EXO 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:16\">EXO 38:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:18\">EXO 38:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:3\">EXO 39:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:5\">EXO 39:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8\">EXO 39:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27\">EXO 39:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:28\">EXO 39:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:28\">EXO 39:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:28\">EXO 39:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:29\">EXO 39:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:22\">PRO 31:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:7\">EZK 27:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： βύσσινος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bussinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:12\">REV 18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:16\">REV 18:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:8\">REV 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:8\">REV 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:14\">REV 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd3:6\">1ES 3:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： βύσσος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bussos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19\">LUK 16:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： λίνον, λινοῦς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： linon, linous)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:6\">REV 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt16:8\">JDT 16:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ὀθόνιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： othonion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:12\">LUK 24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:40\">JHN 19:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:5\">JHN 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:6\">JHN 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:7\">JHN 20:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σινδών</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sindōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:59\">MAT 27:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:51\">MRK 14:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:52\">MRK 14:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:53\">LUK 23:53</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0080_corpse_wrapped_in_linen.png\" alt=\"OAI-0080_corpse_wrapped_in_linen\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>細麻布是由亞麻植物的莖製成的優質布料，非常結實和涼快。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>以色列大多數的亞麻都是從埃及進口，用於製造多種商品。聖經中提到了床罩、船帆、祭司聖服、帳幕器具、葬衣和其他東西。另參《聖經中的植物和樹木》（<em>Plants and Trees in the Bible</em> ）中的<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.1.7 亞麻（亞麻布）（flax [linen]）&lt;FLORA:5.1.7&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>許多語言沒有「亞麻」一詞，翻譯者雖然可以借用外來語，但是在許多情況下，譯文最重要的是突出布料的質量，而不在於原材料是什麼。因此，許多翻譯者使用了「細密的（白）布」或「好布」等短語。在有些語境中，可以將其譯成「由一種植物的纖維製成的布」。翻譯者可能需要添加腳註來予以解釋。</p>\n<p>在幾處經文中，細麻布的重要特點是：與其他布料相比，人不大容易出汗（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27\">EXO 39:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:28\">EXO 39:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:29\">EXO 39:29</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:10\">LEV 6:10</a> ［《和》6:3］，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:17\">EZK 44:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:18\">EZK 44:18</a> ）。如果當地人不知道亞麻布，翻譯者應選擇具有類似特點的布料作為替代。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:59\">MAT 27:59</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:53\">LUK 23:53</a> 中，希臘文<em>sindōn</em> 是指纏裹耶穌的身體以便安葬的布料。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:12\">LUK 24:12</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:40\">JHN 19:40</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:5\">JHN 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:6\">JHN 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:7\">JHN 20:7</a> 中的希臘文<em>othonion</em> 也是這個意思。如果某種語言有專門的詞語表示這種「安葬用布」或「裹屍布」，就應該使用該詞。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
